language Essence 1.3

given g: int(1..)
given s: int(1..)
given w: int(1..)
letting n be g * s
find schedule: matrix indexed by [int(1..w)] of set (size g) of set (size s) of int(1..n)
such that
    and([and([and([and([|g1 intersect g2| <= 1 | g2 <- schedule[w2]]) | g1 <- schedule[w1]]) | w2 : int(w1 + 1..w)])
             | w1 : int(1..w)])

